The package boost-xpressive is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS xpressive)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::xpressive)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_xpressive REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::xpressive)
